textBeforeTable: For more information related to any of the events listed below, please contact the Office of Law Admissions at (419) 772-2211 or by e-mail: lawadmissions@onu.edu. Sorted by State Fall 2014 Recruitment Schedule You are welcome to schedule a personal visit so that we can meet with you individually or visit us at one of the national recruiting events. We hope to see you soon. An ONU College of Law representative is looking forward to meeting with you on campus and across the country as you begin your journey to law school. Meeting with admissions representatives is a helpful way to learn more about the admissions process and all of the wonderful opportunities that ONU Law has to offer. We're headed your way!
